Rating comment: I moved from Long Island to Lincolnton NC and the new home needed a deep clean before I fully moved in. So difficult coming from so far away. I googled house cleaners and this company popped up. I gave them a call, Calvin answered and was so helpful and kind and took all of my information. I was stunned when he asked me if I would like someone to come the next morning since I had furniture to move in and didn’t want to until it was deep cleaned. Calvin set it all up for the next morning!  They showed up exactly as promised and honestly have never ever met harder working, thorough, sweet and determined women as today. I can't thank you enough. I have never ever been able to find someone who would literally clean my home the way they would clean their own, or at least to how I would consider it clean. Hannah and her mom were outstanding. They spent ALL DAY catching every little detail from cleaning all the decorative door frames and base moldings throughout the house to all of the super high and very thick crown molding, numerous ceiling fans, light fixtures and too many blinds to count!  The price was more than fair and actually half of what I have paid for half the work completed in NY. After 8 hours of hard work I even told them they could leave because I felt so bad how hard they worked but they said they wouldn’t feel right if it weren’t complete. I could go on and on about them!!  Thank you so much! I will be reaching out to set up weekly or biweekly service going forward just want to settle in.
